16
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,968
You must be tired, Your Highness.

17
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:30,719
Let me help you change.

18
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,512
Usually,

19
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:39,000
you show such reserve.

20
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,079
Tonight,

21
00:01:42,079 --> 00:01:44,799
I will make sure
you enjoy yourself properly.

22
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,120
Are you rejecting me?

23
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:53,000
Wasn't I

24
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,799
always cherished in your heart?

25
