Who's there?

26
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:28,479
Lu Junxing?

27
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,640
What's wrong?

28
00:02:33,984 --> 00:02:35,104
What are you doing?

29
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,479
Help me.

30
